==================================================
9. BUSINESS RULE ENFORCEMENT
==================================================

Implement backend-side rules for:

- incomplete variation cannot be submitted for review
- variation cannot be ranked with zero reviews
- creator response must belong to the variation’s creator context
- fork requires valid parent variation
- ranking recompute only applies to a valid story
- lineage depth/path must be updated when forking
- forkCount must be maintained consistently

These rules must not exist only in the frontend.

