10. RANKING ENGINE SERVER INTEGRATION
==================================================

Move or mirror the ranking logic so it can run server-side.

Required:
- aggregate all completed reviews for a variation
- compute weighted ranking score
- compute consensus and debated level
- write ranking entries to the database
- update variation rankingState / rankedAt when appropriate

You may expose ranking recomputation as:
- manual endpoint for now
- service callable from submit review flow later

Document the chosen behavior.

==================================================
11. LINEAGE LOGIC SERVER INTEGRATION
==================================================

Implement server-side lineage support.

Required capabilities:
- get ancestor chain
- get descendants or direct children
- generate/maintain path for new forks
- compute depth
- preserve original/source relationships

The backend should be the source of truth for lineage, not the frontend.

